Package: libghostty-vt-dev-tip
Version: GHOSTTY_VERSION-BUILD_VERSION+DIST
Architecture: amd64
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libghostty-vt0-tip (= GHOSTTY_VERSION-BUILD_VERSION+DIST)
Description: Ghostty terminal VT core library (development files, nightly)
 Weekly build of the libghostty-vt development files from the
 upstream main branch. Contains public C headers, the unversioned
 shared library symlink, the static library, and pkg-config files
 required to build applications against libghostty-vt.
 .
 Install the stable `libghostty-vt-dev` package if you want a
 release build.
